Trump's%20defense%20team%20on%20Tuesday%20over%20their%20%26quot%3Banti-Trump%26quot%3B%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20Facebook%20video%20showed%20Manhattanites%20laughing%2C%20cheering%2C%20and%20dancing%20in%20the%20streets%20after%20Joe%20Biden's%202020%20presidential%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20had%20to%20sit%20at%20the%20defense%20table%20and%20watch%20as%20the%20video%20was%20played%20in%20court%2C%20cowbells%20and%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20prospective%20juror%2C%20identified%20only%20as%20%26quot%3BB-133%2C%26quot%3B%20had%20clearly%20%26quot%3Battended%20an%20%26quot%3Banti-Trump%20rally%2C%26quot%3B%20defense%20lawyer%20Susan%20Necheles%20protested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20rally%2C%26quot%3B%20countered%20prosecutor%20Joshua%20Steinglass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seemed%20like%20a%20celebratory%20moment%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20school%20teacher%20stammered%20when%20she%20was%20called%20into%20court%20to%20explain%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20I%20think%20that%20was%20it%2C%20I%20think%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWatching%20New%20Yorkers%20cheer%20in%20the%20streets%20over%20his%20defeat%20appears%20to%20have%20angered%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20Mr.%20Blanche%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20told%20Trump's%20lawyer%2C%20after%20the%20prospective%20juror%20left%20the%20courtroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20juror%20was%20at%20the%20podium%2C%20maybe%2012%20feet%20from%20your%20client%2C%20your%20client%20was%20audibly%20uttering%20something%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20know%20exactly%20what%20he%20was%20uttering%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20won't%20tolerate%20that.%20I%20will%20not%20have%20any%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-scolds-trump-intimidate-jurors-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejurors%20intimidated%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20this%20court