ng%20Israel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20likely%20impact%20(of%20the%20operation)%20is%20that%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20Middle%20East%20Air%20Defense%20(MEAD)%20concept%20will%20convince%20skeptical%20Gulf%20partners%20%E2%80%94%20namely%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20the%20UAE%20%E2%80%94%20that%20an%20American%20concept%20for%20mutual%20defense%20in%20the%20region%20could%20benefit%20them%20as%20much%20as%20it%20did%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20Nicholas%20Heras%2C%20senior%20director%20of%20strategy%20and%20innovation%20at%20the%20New%20Lines%20Institute%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US-led%20operation%20was%20a%20decisive%20factor%20in%20helping%20Israel%20fend%20off%20Iran's%20unprecedented%20April%2013%3Cspan%3E%20drone%20and%20missile%20attack.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20enormous%20strike%20package%20launched%20by%20Iran%20on%20Saturday%20consisted%20of%20an%20estimated%20170%20drones%2C%2030%20cruise%20missiles%2C%20and%20over%20120%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20the%20overwhelming%20majority%20of%20which%20were%20successfully%20interdicted%3B%20there%20are%20also%20reports%20that%20many%20missiles%20failed%20mid-flight%20from%20technical%20problems.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20United%20States%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-countered-iran-attack-israel-fighter-jets-destroyers-patriot-missiles-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshot%20down%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20more%20of%20the%20incoming%20Iranian%20drones%20than%20Israel%20and%20played%20a%20central%20role%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bmultinational%20air%20defense%20operation%26quot%3B%20consisting%20of%20British%2C%20French%2C%20and%20Jordanian%20air%20forces.%20Additionally%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20reportedly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Freport-gulf-states-including-saudi-arabia-provided-intelligence-on-iran-attack%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eprovided%20intelligence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%20Iran's%20attack%20plans.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20has%20been%20pushing%20for%20the%20MEAD%20concept%20since%20its%20early%20days%20in%20office.%20In%20an%20early%20combat%20test%20of%20MEAD%2C%20Israeli%20fighter%20jets%20shot%20down%20two%20incoming%20Iranian%20drones%20outside%20its%20territory%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnational-security%2F2024%2F04%2F15%2Firan-israel-russia-drones-missiles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20Mar.%2015%2C%202021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20in%20cooperation%20with%20unnamed%20Arab%20partners.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224346%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20anti-missile%20system%20operates%20after%20Iran%20launched%20drones%20and%20missiles%20towards%20Israel%2C%20as%20seen%20from%20Ashkelon%2C%20Israel%20on%20April%2014%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6620294d49058e6693570ecd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222899%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20anti-missile%20system%20operates%20after%20Iran%20launched%20drones%20and%20missiles%20towards%20Israel%2C%20as%20seen%20from%20Ashkelon%2C%20Israel%20on%20April%2014%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FAmir%20Cohen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%20oversaw%20a%20similar%20coordinated%20effort%20in%20the%20Iranian%20barrage%20that%20began%20April%2013%20on%20a%20vast%20scale%2C%20bringing%20together%20various%20states%20and%20their%20relevant%20surveillance%20and%20weapons%20systems.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20individual%20weapons%20systems%2C%20while%20important%2C%20are%20less%20decisive%20for%20regional%20decision-making%20than%20the%20reassurance%20that%20the%20United%20States%20will%20be%20there%20to%20coordinate%20the%20use%20of%20the%20weapons%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20Heras%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20the%20Americans%20managing%20the%20regional%20defense%20architecture%2C%20the%20weapons%20systems%20and%20reconnaissance%20equipment%20are%20far%20from%20a%20shield%20for%20Middle%20Eastern%20partners%2C%20including%20Israel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20an%20estimated%2099%25%20of%20the%20Iranian%20munitions%20were%20shot%20down%2C%20and%20reports%20indicated%20others%20failed%20to%20launch%20or%20suffered%20technical%20failures%2C%20Tehran%20does%20not%20consider%20the%20operation%20a%20failure%20%E2%80%94%20far%20from%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIran%20considers%20the%20operation%20a%20success%20beyond%20their%20expectations%2C%26quot%3B%20Farzin%20Nadimi%2C%20a%20defense%20and%20security%20analyst%20and%20senior%20fellow%20of%20the%20Washington%20Institute%20for%20Near%20East%20Policy%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BMore%20than%20anything%2C%20the%20main%20objective%20of%20the%20strike%20was%20to%20create%20a%20new%20paradigm%20that%20Iran%20can%20and%20will%20strike%20directly%20on%20Israeli%20soil%20when%20necessary%2C%26quot%3B%20Nadimi%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20also%20wanted%20to%20establish%20technological%20parity%20with%20Israel%20and%20diminish%20its%20QME%20(qualitative%20military%20edge)%2C%20and%20restore%20their%20credibility%20and%20deterrence%20vs%20Israel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20analyst%20believes%20time%20will%20tell%20if%20Iran%20succeeded%20in%20restoring%20its%20deterrent%20threat%2C%20noting%20that%20another%20important%20objective%20for%20Iran's%20powerful%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20paramilitary%20was%20to%20test%20its%20systems%20against%20Israeli%20and%20allied%20defenses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20consider%20the%20strike%20as%20a%20mere%20message%20to%20Israel%20and%20a%20test%20of%20IRGC's%20offensive%20capabilities%2C%20therefore%20the%20statistics%20(aka%20how%20many%20drones%20and%20missiles%20were%20intercepted%20and%20shot%20down%2C%20or%20the%20extent%20of%20damage%20caused%20by%20those%20that%20made%20impacts%20or%20lack%20thereof)%20become%20of%20lesser%20importance%2C%20if%20any%2C%26quot%3B%20Nadimi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Russia%20Su-35%20Hemeimeem%20Syria%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5d8d07d62e22af664b6a3951%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22933%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Russian%20Su-35%20fighter%20jet%20takes%20off%20at%20Hemeimeem%20air%20base%20in%20Syria%20in%20September%202019.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FAlexander%20Zemlianichenko%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20the%20decisive%20and%20unified%20response%20to%20its%20attack%20influences%20Iran's%20strategy%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%20Iran%20has%20deepened%20its%20military%20ties%20with%20Russia%20since%202022.%20Tehran%20expects%20to%20receive%20Russian%20fighter%20jets%20and%20other%20advanced%20systems%20that%20could%20improve%20its%20air%20defenses%20and%20make%20any%20strike%20on%20Iran%20by%20Israel%20more%20difficult%20and%20dangerous.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BRussia%20will%20seek%20to%20offset%20the%20US%20success%20in%20backing%20Israel%20by%20looking%20to%20buttress%20Iran's%20defense%20with%20advanced%20Russian%20systems%20such%20as%20the%20Su-35%2C%26quot%3B%20Heras%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20intelligence%20officials%2C%20Moscow%20is%20reportedly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnational-security%2F2024%2F04%2F15%2Firan-israel-russia-drones-missiles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3Badvancing%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20agreements%20for%20supplying%20Tehran%20with%20Su-35%20Flanker%20jets%2C%20an%20air%20superiority%20fighter%20that's%20one%20of%20the%20most%20advanced%20in%20Russia's%20arsenal.%20Iran%20confirmed%20it%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Firan-finalises-deal-buy-russian-fighter-jets-tasnim-2023-11-28%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efinalized%20a%20deal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20Su-35s%20and%20Mi-28%20attack%20helicopters%20in%20November.%20There%20were%20also%20reports%20last%20year%20indicating%20Iran%20also%20seeks%20the%20advanced%20Russian%20S-400%20air%20defense%20missile%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BFaster%20delivery%20of%20Russian%20weapons%20such%20as%20Su-35%20or%20S-400%20can%20definitely%20be%20a%20Russian%20answer%20to%20any%20significant%20US%20involvement%20in%20what%20comes%20next%2C%26quot%3B%20Nadimi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%2C%20however%2C%20take%20into%20account%20that%20it%20will%20take%20months%2C%20if%20not%20years%2C%20to%20train%20and%20rate%20combat-ready%20Iranian%20crews%20for%20those%20complex%20systems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-israeli-defeat-irans-missiles-big-boost-for-regional-alliance-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713391112000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662045e120b15f0ff428fa8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-israeli-defeat-irans-missiles-big-boost-for-regional-alliance-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20aerial%20success%20against%20Iran's%20missiles%20was%20a%20major%20boost%20for%20the%20US's%20aim%20of%20a%20defensive%20alliance%20that's%20been%20strained%20by%20Israel's%20