20emphasize%20togetherness%2C%20like%20praying%20at%20community%20mosques%2C%20fasting%20for%20Ramadan%2C%20or%20performing%20the%20Muslim%20pilgrimage%20called%20Hajj.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffeatures.hrw.org%2Ffeatures%2Ffeatures%2Flgbt_laws%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eover%2030%3C%2Fa%3E%20majority-Muslim%20countries%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flgbtq-rights-around-the-world-maps-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecriminalize%20queerness%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20some%20capacity%2C%20many%20Islamic%20scholars%20disagree%20about%20whether%20Islam%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fir.lawnet.fordham.edu%2Fcgi%2Fviewcontent.cgi%3Farticle%3D2322%26context%3Dilj%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccepts%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20queer%20and%20transgender%20people.%20Each%20scholar%2C%20institution%2C%20and%20government%20leads%20with%20their%20own%20interpretation%20of%20and%20perspective%20on%20Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221751%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22LGBT%20Ramadan%20event%20at%20The%20Center%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661fe7de49058e669356e58f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221314%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPerformer%20Kahani%20entertains%20guests%20celebrating%20Ramadan%20at%20New%20York%20City's%20LGBT%20Community%20Center.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dinean%20Robinson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESophia%20Uppal%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20who's%20nonbinary%2C%20described%20their%20relationship%20with%20Islam%20as%20complicated.%20Some%20of%20Uppal's%20favorite%20childhood%20memories%20include%20waking%20up%20early%20to%20their%20mom%20preparing%20sehri%2C%20or%20the%20meal%20Muslims%20eat%20before%20sunrise%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20day's%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20they%20said%20they'd%20also%20felt%20disconnected%20from%20Islam%20for%20so%20long%20because%20of%20the%20expectation%20to%20