C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225394%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Portrait%20of%20LGBTQ%20community%20member%2C%20Dena.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662011df10c6b0cde5f06bda%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224045%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDena%20Igusti%20celebrated%20this%20Ramadan%20with%20fellow%20queer%20Muslims%2C%20saying%20it%20helped%20them%20get%20back%20in%20touch%20with%20their%20faith.%3Cp%3ERamie%20Ahmed%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Dena%20Igusti%2C%20a%2027-year-old%20Indonesian%20Muslim%2C%20gathering%20with%20fellow%20queer%20people%20every%20day%20during%20Ramadan%20allowed%20them%20to%20reconnect%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-show-ramadan-around-the-world-as-muslims-celebrate-holy-holiday%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommunity%20aspect%20of%20Islam%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20enjoyed%20when%20growing%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20my%20first%20Ramadan%20where%20I've%20had%20every%20iftar%20exclusively%20with%20other%20queer%20Muslims%2C%20and%20it%20reminds%20me%20of%20the%20small%20community%20gatherings%20I%20had%20growing%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Igusti%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20gather%20in%20an%20optic%20way%20but%20in%20a%20real%20deep%20sense%20of%20care%20for%20each%20other.%20It%20has%20really%20solidified%20my%20relationship%20with%20Islam%20and%20continued%20to%20show%20me%20the%20beauty%20of%20my%20faith.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFostering%20a%20more%20inclusive%20Muslim%20community%20around%20the%20world%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20very%20few%20examples%20of%20queer%20Muslim%20religious%20leaders%2C%20Imam%20Daayiee%20Abdullah%2C%2070%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Mecca%20Institute%2C%20and%20his%20ethos%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20tell%20anyone%20they%20are%20a%20Muslim%3B%20they%20tell%20us%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0ha