er%20prime%20minister%20Imran%20Khan%20on%20Wednesday%20alleged%20that%20Army%20chief%20General%20Asim%20Munir%20was%20directly%20responsible%20for%20the%20imprisonment%20of%20his%20wife%20Bushra%20Bibi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBushra%20Bibi%2C%2049%2C%20was%20convicted%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20case%20of%20illegal%20marriage%20with%20Mr%20Khan%2C%2071%2C%20and%20is%20currently%20held%20in%20detention%20at%20their%20Bani%20Gala%20residence%20in%20the%20suburbs%20of%20Islamabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20leader%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20journalists%20at%20Adiala%20Jail%20where%20he%20is%20currently%20incarcerated%20hurled%20allegations%20on%20the%20army%20chief%2C%20according%20to%20a%20long%20post%20uploaded%20on%20Mr%20Khan's%20official%20X%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGeneral%20Asim%20Munir%20is%20directly%20involved%20in%20the%20sentence%20awarded%20to%20my%20wife%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Khan%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20judge%20who%20convicted%20her%20said%20that%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20make%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20anything%20happens%20to%20my%20wife%2C%20I%20will%20not%20leave%20Asim%20Munir%2C%20I%20will%20not%20leave%20Asim%20Munir%20as%20long%20as%20I%20am%20alive.%20I%20will%20expose%20his%20unconstitutional%20and%20illegal%20steps%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20threatened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khan%20said%20there%20was%20a%20law%20of%20the%20jungle%20in%20the%20country%20and%20all%20was%20being%20done%20by%20the%20%26quot%3Bking%20of%20the%20jungle%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20king%20of%20the%20jungle%20wants%2C%20all%20the%20cases%20of%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20are%20forgiven%2C%20and%20when%20he%20wants%2C%20we%20are%20punished%20in%20three%20cases%20in%20five%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khan%20also%20said%20that%20the%20economy%20would%20stabilise%20not%20through%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20(IMF)%20loans%20but%20by%20investment.%20%26quot%3BDue%20to%20the%20law%20of%20the%20jungle%2C%20there%20will%20be%20no%20investment%20in%20the%20country.%20It%20is%20good%20that%20Saudi%20Arabia%20is%20coming%20but%20investment%20will%20come%20once%20there%20is%20rule%20of%20law%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20recent%20reported%20clash%20between%20police%20and%20army%20in%20Bahawalnagar%20area%20of%20Punjab%20and%20said%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bpolice%20were%20thrashed%26quot%3B%20by%20violating%20the%20law%2C%20but%20the%20IG%20(inspector%20general%20police)%20and%20Viceroy%2C%20who%20oppressed%20our%20people%2C%20apologised%20from%20those%20who%20had%20thrashed%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khan%20said%20the%20Viceroy%20said%20after%20the%20incident%20that%20%26quot%3Bthey%20(police)%20are%20our%20brothers%26quot%3B.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20%26quot%3Bsuch%20treatment%20is%20done%20to%20slaves%20and%20not%20to%20brothers%26quot%3B%20because%20those%20having%20power%20thrashed%20the%20police%20and%20also%20forced%20to%20apologise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20PTI%20was%20being%20stopped%20from%20contesting%20in%20the%20by-elections.%20%26quot%3BAt%20this%20time%2C%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20oppression%20is%20Jihad.%20Our%20workers%20have%20to%20protect%20each%20vote%2C%20guard%20the%20vote%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20premier%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%20the%20army%20has%20not%20responded%20to%20the%20serious%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713380640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fia818iug_imran-khan-afp_625x300_19_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fif-anything-happens-to-my-wife-ex-pak-pm-imran-khan-warns-