aoist)%20as%20a%20child%20and%20despite%20the%20family%20members%20trying%20to%20persuade%20him%20to%20quit%2C%20he%20stayed%20with%20the%20Maoist%20movement%2C%20Lingaram%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20was%20yet%20to%20contact%20the%20police%20to%20claim%20Sukku's%20body%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20route%20to%20the%20encounter%20site%2C%20mostly%20dirt%20roads%20or%20forest%20paths%2C%20was%20dug%20up%20at%20multiple%20locations.%20Maoist%20posters%20calling%20on%20locals%20to%20boycott%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20crude%20memorials%20for%20killed%20Maoists%20could%20be%20seen%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20reach%20the%20area%2C%20considered%20a%20stronghold%20of%20the%20North%20Bastar%20Division%20Committee%20of%20Maoists%2C%20one%20has%20to%20cross%20the%20Kotri%20river%20which%20runs%20dry%20in%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20local%20administration%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20construct%20a%20bridge%20on%20the%20river%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20but%20the%20work%20did%20not%20make%20any%20progress%20as%20villagers%20are%20opposed%20to%20it%2C%20an%20official%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20encounter%20site%20is%20located%20more%20than%2015%20km%20from%20Bechaghat%20on%20the%20tri-junction%20of%20Kanker%20and%20Narayanpur%20districts%20of%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Gadchiroli%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAaytu%2C%20a%20villager%2C%20said%20he%20heard%20gunshots%20on%20Tuesday%20afternoon%20from%20a%20hill%20adjoining%20Kalpar%20village.%20He%2C%20however%2C%20was%20not%20willing%20to%20elaborate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20climbing%20the%20hill%2C%20which%20has%20thick%20bamboo%20vegetation%2C%20blood%20stains%20and%20bullet%20marks%20on%20trees%20could%20be%20seen%20in%20places.%20Empty%20syringes%20and%20bottles%20of%20soft%20drinks%20and%20a%20makeshift%20stretcher%20used%20by%20the%20security%20personnel%20to%20ferry%20their%20injured%20colleagues%20were%20lying%20in%20a%20dry%20rivulet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3