-awaits-israels-response-to-iran-with-fears-growing-revenge-will-trigger-bigger-war-13117455%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Flebanon-at-a-crossroads-as-it-awaits-israels-response-to-iran-with-fears-growing-revenge-will-trigger-bigger-war-13117455%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Men%20Chant%20'Jai%20Shri%20Ram'%20In%20Car%20On%20Ram%20Navami%2C%20Thrashed%20By%204%20In%20Bengaluru%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20people%20have%20been%20injured%20in%20Bengaluru%20after%20an%20argument%20broke%20out%20between%20them%20and%20four%20others%2C%20allegedly%20over%20chanting%20%3Cem%3E'Jai%20Shri%20Ram'%3C%2Fem%3E.%20A%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20and%20two%20accused%20have%20been%20arrested%20while%20two%20others%20-%20at%20least%20one%20of%20whom%20is%20a%20minor%20-%20have%20been%20detained%20on%20charges%20of%20hurting%20religious%20feelings%20and%20rioting%2C%20among%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20officials%20said%20three%20men%2C%20identified%20as%20Pavan%20Kumar%2C%20Rahul%20and%20Binayak%2C%20were%20in%20a%20car%20and%20were%20going%20to%20inspect%20a%20second-hand%20two-wheeler%20that%20was%20on%20sale.%20They%20had%20a%20saffron%20flag%20and%20were%20chanting%20%3Cem%3E'Jai%20Shri%20Ram'%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20when%20Ram%20Navami%20was%20celebrated%2C%20said%20an%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%203.45%20pm%2C%20two%20men%20on%20a%20bike%2C%20identified%20as%20Farman%20and%20Sameer%2C%20stopped%20them%20in%20North%20Bengaluru's%20Chikkabettahalli%20and%20asked%20why%20they%20were%20chanting%20the%20slogan%2C%20saying%20that%20they%20should%20only%20shout%20%3Cem%3E'Allahu%20Akbar'%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20according%20to%20the%20first%20information%20report%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFarman%20then%20tried%20to%20snatch%20the%20flag%20from%20the%20three%20men%2C%20two%20of%20whom%20chased%20him%20into%20a%20lane.%20Sameer%20rode%20away.%20The%20three%20men%20returned%20to%20their%20ca