2Maldives%20President%20Muizzu%20Accused%20Of%20Corruption%20In%20Leaked%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20parliamentary%20polls%20in%20the%20Maldives%2C%20the%20opposition%20parties%20have%20demanded%20a%20probe%20and%20impeachment%20of%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20following%20the%20leaked%20report%20of%20his%20alleged%20corruption%20from%202018%2C%20a%20charge%20dismissed%20by%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElections%20to%20the%20Majlis%20are%20to%20be%20held%20on%20Sunday%20and%20the%20atmosphere%20has%20been%20vitiated%20by%20the%20trading%20of%20charges%20between%20the%20main%20opposition%20the%20Maldivian%20Democratic%20Party%20(MDP)%20and%20the%20Muizzu's%20People's%20National%20Congress%20(PNC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20media%20reports%20have%20highlighted%20that%20the%20political%20storm%20started%20on%20Monday%20with%20an%20anonymous%20handle%20'Hassan%20Kurusee'%20posting%20on%20social%20media%20X%20leaked%20intelligence%20reports%2C%20including%20documents%20prepared%20by%20the%20Financial%20Intelligence%20Unit%20(FIU)%20of%20the%20Maldives%20Monetary%20Authority%20and%20the%20Maldives%20Police%20Service%20that%20allegedly%20linked%20President%20Muizzu%20to%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20reports%2C%20dated%20circa%202018%2C%20claim%20irregularities%20in%20money%20transfers%20to%20President%20Muizzu's%20personal%20bank%20account%2C%20highlighting%2010%20critical%20red%20flag%20indicators%20of%20financial%20misconduct.%20These%20indicators%20suggest%20involvement%20with%20politically%20exposed%20persons%2C%20embezzlement%2C%20structured%20transactions%2C%20and%20the%20use%20of%20corporate%20entities%20to%20hide%20fund%20origins%2C%26quot%3B%20news%20portal%20Maldives%20Republic%20(mvrepublic.com)%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20soon%20created%20a%20political%20storm%20with%20several%20reactions%20pouring%20in%20on%20various%20social%20media%20channels.%20News%20portals%20and%20newspapers%2C%20however%2C%20tread%20with%20caution.%20The%20opposition%20Maldivian%20Democratic%20Party%20(MDP)%20and%20People's%20National%20Front%20(PNF)%20demanded%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Vice%20President%20Dr%20Mohamed%20Jameel%20Ahmed%20urged%20Muizzu's%20impeachment%20following%20the%20leaked%20intelligence%20reports.%20Taking%20to%20his%20social%20media%20handle%20X%2C%20Jameel%20reposted%20these%20documents%2C%20emphasising%20the%20need%20for%20accountability%20at%20all%20levels%20of%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20demanding%20Muizzu's%20impeachment%2C%20Jameel%2C%20a%20senior%20member%20of%20the%20Progressive%20Party%20of%20Maldives%2C%20%26quot%3Balso%20accused%20President%20Muizzu%20of%20extensive%20corruption%20in%20his%20flagship%20Ras%20Male'%20development%20project%20and%20alleged%20excessive%20spending%20on%20public%20relations.%20Jameel%20has%20called%20on%20President%20Muizzu%20to%20cooperate%20with%20independent%20investigations%20into%20these%20allegations%2C%26quot%3B%20mvrepublic.com%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20portal%20also%20claimed%20that%20this%20was%20the%20first%20time%20an%20FIU%20report%20was%20leaked%20and%20said%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20official%20confirmation%20or%20response%20from%20government%20bodies%20regarding%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20reports%20or%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdhadhu.com%20reported%20that%20President%20Muizzu%20responded%20late%20on%20Tuesday%20night%20to%20corruption%20allegations%20declaring%20that%20the%20opposition%20%26quot%3Bcannot%20show%20any%20wrongdoing%20on%20his%20part%20regardless%20of%20how%20far%20attempts%20to%20implicate%20him%20are%20taken%26quot%3B%20and%20also%20accused%20the%20opposition%20of%20leaking%20the%20reports%20out%20of%20desperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20same%20allegations%20had%20been%20made%20during%20his%20campaigns%20for%20mayor%20and%20President%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20adding%2C%20the%20response%20would%20also%20be%20the%20same%20as%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20you%20attempt%20to%20pin%20something%20on%20me%20like%20this%2C%20you%20couldn't%20do%20it%20before%20and%20you%20can't%20do%20it%20now.%20There's%20nothing%20you%20can%20show%20against%20me%20no%20matter%20how%20far%20you%20take%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Adhadhu.com%20said%2C%20quoting%20the%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtoll%20Times%20gave%20a%20detailed%20account%20of%20what%20President%20Muizzu%20said%20in%20his%20defence%2C%20including%20how%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bnever%20compromise%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20people%20and%20that%20no%20matter%20how%20many%20such%20allegations%20are%20made%2C%20nobody%20will%20be%20able%20to%20show%20anything%20done%20in%20such%20a%20manner.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20last%20five%20years%20opposition%20was%20in%20government%2C%20if%20there%20was%20anything%20done%20wrong%2C%20it%20would%20have%20come%20to%20light%2C%26quot%3B%20Muizzu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20President's%20remarks%20came%20after%20the%20opposition%20Maldivian%20Democratic%20Party%20(MDP)%20and%20People's%20National%20Front%20(PNF)%20called%20on%20the%20relevant%20authorities%20to%20investigate%20the%20serious%20allegations%20against%20the%20President.%20But%20no%20government%20investigative%20agency%20has%20yet%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20Adhadhu.com%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%20368%20candidates%20are%20contesting%20for%2093%20seats%20in%20this%20year's%20parliamentary%20elections%20on%20April%2021%2C%20according%20to%20media%20reports.%20The%20outcome%20of%20the%20elections%20will%20determine%20whether%20the%20opposition%20parties%20can%20act%20against%20President%20Muizzu%2C%20who%20assumed%20charge%20in%20November%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%