etary%20Janet%20Yellen%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20easy%20to%20find%20a%20leader%20with%20the%20skill%20and%20drive%20to%20take%20on%20the%20monumental%20task%20of%20transforming%20an%20essential%20institution%2C%20but%20since%20becoming%20World%20Bank%20president%20last%20June%2C%20Ajay%20Banga%20has%20done%20just%20that.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20Banga%20came%20to%20the%20World%20Bank%20after%20leading%20a%20global%20organisation%20through%20which%20he%20brought%20millions%20of%20unbanked%20people%20into%20the%20digital%20economy.%20At%20the%20World%20Bank%2C%20he%20set%20forth%20a%20new%20vision%20to%20create%20a%20world%20free%20of%20poverty%20on%20a%20livable%20planet%20and%20moved%20boldly%20to%20make%20good%20on%20it%20-%20from%20pioneering%20innovative%20financial%20tools%20to%20reimagining%20partnerships%20across%20the%20multilateral%20development%20banks%20and%20with%20the%20private%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20sharp%20wit%20consistently%20enables%20him%20to%20cut%20through%20the%20noise.%20With%20unprecedented%20challenges%20such%20as%20climate%20change%20threatening%20our%20collective%20future%2C%20I%20cannot%20imagine%20a%20better%20partner%20with%20whom%20to%20take%20decisive%20action%20on%20behalf%20of%20people%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Yellen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20Bhatt%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bformidable%20talent%26quot%3B%2C%20director%2C%20producer%20and%20writer%20Tom%20Harper%20said%20in%20the%20Time%20profile%20that%20she%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20only%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20leading%20actors%2C%20admired%20for%20her%20work%20in%20the%20Indian%20film%20industry%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20-%20she%20is%20also%20a%20businesswoman%20and%20a%20philanthropist%20who%20leads%20with%20integrity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlia's%20superpower%20is%20her%20ability%20to%20mix%20movie-star%20magnetism%20with%20authenticity%20and%20sensitivity.%20As%20an%20actor%20she%20is%20luminous%2C%20and%20as%20a%20person%20she%20brings%20the%20grounded%20assurance%20and%20creativity%20that%20make%20a%20truly%20international%20star%2C%26quot%3B%20Harper%2C%20who%20directed%20Bhatt%20in%20his%20movie%20'Heart%20of%20Stone'%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Nadella%2C%20Time%20said%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bprofoundly%20influential%20in%20shaping%20our%20future.%20And%20that's%20a%20good%20thing%20for%20humanity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMicrosoft's%20significant%20investment%20in%20OpenAI%20and%20partnership%20with%20Mistral%20AI%20puts%20him%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20artificial%20intelligence%20revolution.%20A%20technologist%20with%20heart%2C%20Satya%20sees%20AI%20as%20a%20tool%20that%20will%20empower%20humans.%20Still%2C%20there's%20rightful%20concern%20about%20unintended%20consequences%20and%20misuse.%20That's%20why%20it's%20so%20reassuring%20that%20Satya%20is%20one%20of%20AI's%20stewards.%20His%20thoughtfulness%20and%20humility%20should%20make%20us%20safer%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sakshi%20Malik%2C%20Oscar-nominated%20documentary%20filmmaker%20Nisha%20Pahuja%20writes%20that%20she%20was%20among%20India's%20%26quot%3Bmost%20celebrated%20wrestlers%26quot%3B%20who%20had%20gathered%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%20in%20Delhi%20in%20early%202023%20to%20demand%20the%20immediate%20arrest%20and%20resignation%20of%20the%20then-chief%20of%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%2C%20accused%20of%20sexually%20harassing%20female%20athletes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20began%20as%20a%20small%2C%20targeted%20protest%20to%20demand%20decisive%20government%20action%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20wrestlers%20ballooned%20instead%20into%20a%20yearlong%20battle%20unprecedented%20in%20Indian%20sport%2C%20drawing%20support%20from%20across%20the%20country%20and%20attention%20from%20across%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Pahuja%20writes%20in%20her%20profile%20of%20Malik%20for%20Time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20fight%20is%20no%20longer%20only%20for%20India's%20female%20wrestlers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20of%20the%20movement%20Malik%20helped%20spark%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20for%20the%20daughters%20of%20India%20whose%20voices%20have%20been%20silenced%20time%20and%20again%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShortly%20after%20Singh's%20successor%2C%20a%20close%20ally%20and%20business%20partner%2C%20was%20elected%20to%20oversee%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%2C%20Sakshi%20Malik%20-%20in%20an%20emotional%2C%20public%2C%20and%20very%20brave%20act%20of%20defiance%20-%20quit%20the%20sport.%20She%20did%20not%2C%20however%2C%20quit%20the%20battle.%20Her%20light%2C%20and%20the%20light%20of%20all%20those%20standing%20against%20harassment%2C%20continues%20to%20shine%2C%26quot%3B%20Pahuja%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Patel%2C%20the%20Time%20profile%20by%20Oscar-winning%20actor%20Daniel%20Kaluuya%20said%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bradiates%20goodness.%20His%20humanity%20shines%20through%20every%20time%20he%20graces%20the%20screen%2C%20leaving%20you%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20root%20for%20him%20even%20when%20his%20character%20is%20doing%20something%20foul%3B%20his%20presence%20makes%20you%20understand%20where%20he's%20coming%20from%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel%20made%20his%20directorial%20debut%20with%20'Monkey%20Man'.%20%26quot%3BDev%20sets%20the%20pace.%20He's%20limitless.%20He's%20fearless.%20Our%20responsibility%20as%20a%20generation%20is%20to%20go%20into%20familiar%20spaces%20and%20see%20them%20through%20new%20perspectives%2C%20thus%20creating%2C%20finding%2C%20and%20sharing%20a%20space%20that%20has%20never%20been%20touched%20before.%20He%20has%20that%20gift.%20He%20continues%20to%20surpass%20himself%20and%20surprise%20us%2C%20and%20we%20are%20all%20waiting%20for%20where%20he'll%20take%20us%20next%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShep%20Doeleman%2C%20an%20astrophysicist%20and%20the%20founding%20director%20of%20the%20Event%20Horizon%20Telescope%2C%20wrote%20in%20the%20profile%20for%20Natarajan%20that%20a%20novel%20approach%20developed%20years%20ago%20by%20her%20%26quot%3Bbrought%20us%20closer%20to%20understanding%20a%20basic%20mystery%20in%20astronomy%3A%20How%20do%20the%20supermassive%20black%20holes%20that%20lurk%20at%20the%20centres%20of%20most%20galaxies%20form%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BPriya%20has%20a%20knack%20for%20pursuing%20the%20most%20creative%20research%2C%20and%20as%20a%20fellow%20astronomer%2C%20I%20am%20always%20inspired%20by%20her%20work.%20Her%20latest%20result%20takes%20us%20one%20step%20closer%20to%20understanding%20our%20cosmic%20beginnings%2C%26quot%3B%20Doeleman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713372000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-08%2Fvads2fo8_sakshi-malik_625x300_22_August_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmicrosoft-ceo-satya-nadella-alia-bhatt-on-times-100-most-influential-list-5463634%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22World%20Bank%20President%20Ajay%20Banga%2C%20Bollywood%20actor%20Alia%20Bhatt%2C%20Microsoft%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella%2C%20Olympian%20wrestler%20Sakshi%20Malik%20and%20actor%20Dev%20Patel%20are%20among%20the%20Indians%20who%20have%20made%20it%20to%20the%20prestigious%20Times's%20list%20of%20100%20most%20influential%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmicrosoft-ceo-satya-nadella-alia-bhatt-on-times-100-most-influential-list-5463634%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmicrosoft-ceo-satya-nadella-alia-bhatt-on-times-100-most-influential-list-5463634%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmicro