ia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109380562.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKaran%20shared%20a%20cute%20video%20of%20Yash%20beatboxing%2C%20interrupted%20by%20Roohi.%20Doubts%20talent%20inheritance.%20Single%20parent%20to%20Yash%20and%20Roohi%20through%20surrogacy%20in%202017.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkaran-johar-drops-a-video-of-his-kids-yash-and-roohi-trying-beatboxing-i-havent-transferred-my-musical-genes-watch%2Farticleshow%2F109380562.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22There%20Is%20No%20Substitute%20For%20Hard%20Work%2C%20Says%20UPSC%20Rank%20Holder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC)%20announced%20the%20results%20of%20the%20Civil%20Services%20Examination%20(CSE)%202023%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20bringing%20joy%20to%20many%20aspirants%20and%20boosting%20the%20morale%20of%20those%20preparing%20for%20the%20exam.%20Inspiring%20stories%20of%20perseverance%20and%20patience%20are%20emerging%20from%20candidates%20who%20successfully%20cleared%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20toughest%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%201%2C016%20candidates%20-%20664%20men%20and%20352%20women%20-%20cleared%20the%20examination%20and%20have%20been%20recommended%20for%20appointment%20to%20various%20services.%20These%20success%20stories%20not%20only%20inspire%20aspiring%20candidates%20but%20also%20people%20from%20different%20walks%20of%20life%20to%20strive%20for%20remarkable%20achievements%20with%20dedication%20and%20determination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20qualifiers%2C%20Prerna%20Singh%20secured%20the%20271st%20rank.%20She%20attended%20classes%20for%20the%20civil%20services%20exam%20at%20Jamia%20Millia%20Islamia's%20Residential%20Coaching%20Academy%2C%20which%20offers%20free%20coaching%20to%20aspirants.%20In%20her%20second%20attempt%2C%20Ms%20Singh%20cleared%20the%20UPSC%20civil%20services%20examination.%20Hailing%20from%20Jharkhand%2C%20she%20is%20an%20alumna%20of%20Delhi%20University's%20Miranda%20House%20College.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Singh%20completed%20her%20schooling%20at%20Delhi%20Public%20School%2C%20Ranchi%2C%20and%20graduated%20in%20Sociology%20from%20Miranda%20House%20College.%20She%20pursued%20a%20post-graduation%20in%20Social%20Work%20from%20Jamia%20Millia%20Islamia.%20Following%20her%20graduation%2C%20she%20worked%20as%20an%20assistant%20manager%20HR%20at%20Vedanta%2C%20BALCO%2C%20for%20about%20a%20year%20before%20deciding%20to%20quit%20her%20job%20and%20prepare%20for%20civil%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UPSC%20rank%20holder%20faced%20an%20emotional%20setback%20due%20to%20her%20father's%20untimely%20death%2C%20yet%20she%20found%20invaluable%20support%20from%20her%20mother%20to%20pursue%20her%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV.com%20reached%20out%20to%20her%20for%20insights%20into%20her%20examination%20preparation%20and%20how%20she%20managed%20to%20crack%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20was%20your%20key%20strategy%20for%20preparing%20for%20UPSC%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20to%20focus%20on%20three%20things%20-%20the%20syllabus%2C%20previous%20years'%20questions%2C%20and%20multiple%20revisions.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20I%20focused%20on%20solving%20test%20series%20for%20both%20prelims%20and%20mains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%20whom%20do%20you%20want%20to%20give%20credit%20for%20your%20success%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20believe%20whatever%20I%20am%20today%2C%20whatever%20good%20I%20will%20do%20in%20the%20future%2C%20it's%20all%20because%20of%20my%20mother.%20After%20my%20father's%20premature%20demise%2C%20my%20mother's%20unwavering%20support%20helped%20me%20fulfil%20my%20goals.%20During%20this%20preparation%2C%20she%20not%20only%20helped%20me%20financially%20but%20also%20emotionally.%20I%20truly%20believe%20this%20is%20her%20success%20more%20than%20mine.%20Apart%20from%20her%2C%20my%20friend%20Ayushi%20has%20been%20a%20constant%20source%20of%20support%20and%20motivation%20for%20me%20in%20this%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20your%20message%20for%20UPSC%20aspirants%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20message%20for%20other%20aspirants%20would%20be%20that%20they%20should%20have%20an%20answer%20for%20why%20they%20want%20to%20take%20this%20exam.%20This%20would%20be%20the%20source%20of%20their%20constant%20motivation%20during%20this%20journey.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20I%20believe%20this%20exam%20requires%20a%20sense%20of%20discipline%20and%20patience%2C%20if%20you%20are%20not%20clearing%20it%20please%20don't%20get%20disheartened.%20Your%20success%20is%20just%20delayed%20and%20not%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20your%20aim%20after%20becoming%20a%20public%20servant%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20public%20servant%2C%20my%20main%20aim%20is%20to%20work%20with%20people%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level.%20I%20have%20always%20been%20inclined%20towards%20the%20social%20sector%20and%20I%20believe%20civil%20services%20offer%20a%20platform%20to%20systematically%20work%20in%20this%20direction.%20I%20want%20to%20act%20as%20a%20catalyst%20for%20women-led%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20key%20to%20success%20in%20the%20UPSC%20Civil%20Services%20Exam%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20to%20success%20I%20would%20say%20is%20consistency%20and%20patience.%20There%20is%20no%20substitute%20for%20hard%20work.%20This%20exam%20takes%20time%20and%20one%20should%20be%20aware%20of%20this%20before%20deciding%20to%20attempt%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20see%20Jamia%20Millia%20Islamia's%20Residential%20Coaching%20Academy%20for%20UPSC%20aspirants%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20honest%20I%20believe%2C%20Jamia's%20residential%20coaching%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20places%20to%20prepare%20for%20civil%20services%20in%20this%20country.%20The%20learning%20environment%20one%20gets%20here%2C%20peer-to-peer%20discussions%2C%20basic%20facilities%20like%20hostel%2C%20library%20etc.%20all%20provide%20a%20very%20conducive%20environment%20for%20an%20aspirant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20were%20your%20Prelims%2C%20Mains%2C%20and%20Interviews%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%20the%20prelims%20paper%20was%20slightly%20tricky.%20But%20I%20had%20faith%20in%20my%20preparation.%20I%20was%20confident%20of%20clearing%20the%201st%20stage.%20This%20was%20my%202nd%20Mains%20and%20I%20worked%20hard%20this%20time%20to%20improve%20my%20answer%20writing%20skills.%20From%20solving%20multiple%20test%20series%20to%20focusing%20on%20better%20structuring%20of%20answers%2C%20I%20tried%20everything.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20attempt%20all%20the%20questions%20in%20all%20the%20papers.%20The%20last%20stage%20was%20an%20interview%20round.%20I%20prepared%20my%20Detailed%20Application%20Form%20(DAF)%20thoroughly.%20The%20interview%20experience%20was%20one%20of%20a%20kind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20basic%20elements%20needed%20to%20become%20a%20topper%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20toppers%20do%20different%20things%2C%20but%2C%20definitely%2C%20consistency%20in%20preparation%20and%20discipline%20are%20needed%20for%20anybody%20to%20clear%20this%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20many%20hours%20should%20aspiring%20students%20dedicate%20to%20study%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20a%20timetable%20where%20I%20studied%207-8%20hours%20daily.%20When%20the%20exam%20dates%20were%20approaching%2C%20the%20number%20of%20hours%20would%20automatically%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20was%20your%20sociology%20subject%20in%20the%20exams%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20optional%20is%20sociology.%20Apart%20from%20that%2C%20the%20other%20subjects%20were%20common%20as%20other%20aspirants%20including%20Indian%20polity%2C%20Economics%2C%20History%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20see%20students%20from%20science%20and%20arts%20backgrounds%20aiding%20them%20in%20clearing%20UPSC%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20would%20say%20that%20the%20UPSC%20has%20designed%20the%20syllabus%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20that%20both%20science%20and%20art%20students%20have%20certain%20advantages.%20For%20eg-%20CSAT%20is%20considered%20to%20give%20an%20advantage%20to%20science%20and%20engineering%20students%20while%20mains%20paper%20like%20essays%20gives%20a%20slight%20advantage%20to%20art%20students.%20However%2C%20these%20differences%20don't%20matter%20much.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20an%20aspirant%20has%20to%20align%20her%2Fhis%20preparation%20as%20per%20the%20demand%20of%20the%20exam%20pattern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20is%20the%20right%20time%20for%20a%20student%20to%20start%20preparing%20for%20UPSC%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20right%20time%2C%20it%20varies%20from%20student%20to%20student.%20For%20some%2C%20it%20is%20just%20after%20the%2012th%20while%20for%20others%20is%20after%20they%20have%20gained%20some%20work%20experience.%20I%20would%20say%20that%20the%20right%20time%20is%20when%20you%20have%20found%20your%20answer%20for%20%26quot%3Bwhy%26quot%3B%20civil%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20kind%20of%20books%20and%20study%20materials%20would%20you%20recommend%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20books%20I%20referred%20to%20are%20the%20basics%20one%20which%20everyone%20has%20access%20to.%20For%20instance%2C%20Lakshmi%20Kant%20for%20Polity%2C%20Spectrum%20For%20Modern%20History%20etc.%20I%20would%20suggest%20that%20you%20keep%20your%20sources%20limited%20and%20revise%20the%20same%20source%20multiple%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713370020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndt