ic%20holiday%20under%20section%2025%20of%20the%20Negotiable%20Instruments%20Act%201881%20to%20facilitate%20the%20electoral%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20Labour%20Welfare%20and%20Skill%20Development%20Department%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20mandated%20a%20paid%20holiday%20for%20all%20employees%20working%20in%20shops%2C%20commercial%20establishments%2C%20industrial%20establishments%20and%20IT%20companies%20on%20April%2019%20to%20ensure%20their%20participation%20in%20the%20democratic%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20the%20directive%2C%20it%20has%20come%20to%20our%20notice%20that%20online%20delivery%20platforms%20such%20as%20Flipkart%20and%20Big%20Basket%20are%20continuing%20to%20guarantee%20delivery%20services%20on%20April%2019.%20This%20raises%20serious%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20infringement%20of%20delivery%20personnel's%20rights%2C%20particularly%20those%20who%20are%20integral%20to%20the%20operations%20of%20these%20platforms%2C'%20the%20complaint%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant%20has%20demanded%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20claims%20of%20e-commerce%20of%20guaranteed%20delivery%20on%20voting%20day%20and%20to%20take%20appropriate%20measures%20to%20uphold%20the%20democratic%20rights%20of%20all%20workers%20irrespective%20of%20their%20state%20of%20origin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%2C%20Flipkart%20said%20it%20is%20giving%20paid%20holidays%20to%20only%20eligible%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20Flipkart%20group%2C%20we're%20following%20all%20the%20directives%20and%20guidelines%20provided%20by%20the%20authorities%20with%20regard%20to%20polling%20day%2C%20and%20are%20giving%20all%20eligible%20employees%20a%20paid%20holiday%20to%20exercise%20their%20franchise.%20In%20addition%2C%20we%20have%20taken%20steps%20to%20drive%20awareness%20and%20encourage%20employees%20to%20vote%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Flipkart%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2