cal-phdcci-124041700752_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findian-economy-likely-to-register-8-8-3-growth-in-current-fiscal-phdcci-124041700752_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findian-economy-likely-to-register-8-8-3-growth-in-current-fiscal-phdcci-124041700752_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20Notifies%20New%20FDI%20Rules%20For%20Space%20Sector%20Ahead%20Of%20Elon%20Musk's%20Visit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20notified%20amendments%20to%20the%20foreign%20direct%20investment%20policy%20in%20the%20space%20sector%20to%20attract%20offshore%20investors%20in%20satellite%20manufacturing%20and%20satellite%20launch%20vehicles%20segments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmendment%20made%20in%20the%20FDI%20policy%20for%20space%20sector%20through%20a%20gazette%20notification%20dated%20April%2016%2C%202024%2C%20prescribes%20liberalized%20entry%20route%20and%20provides%20clarity%20for%20FDI%20in%20satellites%2C%20launch%20vehicles%20and%20associated%20systems%20or%20subsystems%2C%20creation%20of%20spaceports%20for%20launching%20and%20receiving%20Spacecraft%20and%20manufacturing%20of%20space-related%20components%20and%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20rules%20may%20be%20called%20the%20Foreign%20Exchange%20Management%20(Non-debt%20Instruments)%20(Third%20Amendment)%20Rules%2C%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20gazette%20notification%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20liberalized%20entry%20routes%20under%20the%20amended%20policy%20are%20aimed%20at%20attracting%20potential%20investors%20in%20the%20Indian%20companies%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Cabinet%20earlier%20this%20year%20gave%20approval%20to%20these%20amendments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20comes%20days%20ahead%20of%20the%20scheduled%20visit%20of%20Tesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20who%20is%20expected%20to%20meet%20with%20various%20Indian%20space%20companies%20during%20his%20visit%20from%20April%2021%20to%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcurrently%2C%20approvals%20for%20Musk's%20satellite%20internet%20project%2C%20Starlink%2C%20are%20nearing%20finalization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20notification%2C%20up%20to%2074%20per%20cent%20FDI%20for%20satellite%20manufacturing%20%26amp%3B%20operation%2C%20satellite%20data%20products%20and%20ground%20segment%20%26amp%3B%20user%20segment%20are%20allowed%20under%20automatic%20route.%20Beyond%2074%20per%20cent%20these%20activities%20are%20under%20government%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFDI%20up%20to%2049%20per%20cent%20is%20allowed%20for%20Launch%20Vehicles%20and%20associated%20systems%20or%20subsystems%2C%20Creation%20of%20Spaceports%20for%20launching%20and%20receiving%20Spacecraft%20are%20under%20automatic%20route%20but%20beyond%2049%20per%20cent%20government%20permission%20would%20be%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20100%20per%20cent%20FDI%20allowed%20for%20manufacturing%20of%20components%20and%20systems%2F%20sub-systems%20for%20satellites%2C%20ground%20segment%20and%20user%20segment%20without%20government%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20earlier%20norms%2C%20FDI%20was%20permitted%20in%20establishment%20and%20operation%20of%20Satellites%20through%20the%20government%20approval%20route%20only.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20line%20with%20the%20vision%20and%20strategy%20under%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Policy%202023%2C%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%20has%20eased%20the%20FDI%20policy%20in%20the%20Space%20sector%20by%20prescribing%20liberalized%20FDI%20thresholds%20for%20various%20sub-sectors%2Factivities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Space%20consulted%20with%20internal%20stakeholders%20like%20IN-SPACe%2C%20ISRO%20and%20NSIL%20as%20well%20as%20several%20industrial%20stakeholders.%20NGEs%20have%20developed%20capabilities%20and%20expertise%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20satellites%20and%20la