0the%20Maoists%20would%20be%20present%20at%20the%20first%20point%2C%20but%20they%20were%20not%20there.%20We%20searched%20for%20another%20spot%20and%20found%20cooking%20utensils.%20We%20had%20info%20that%2015-20%20are%20present%2C%20but%20around%2035%20rebels%20were%20up%20on%20the%20hill%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20searched%20to%20find%20them%2C%20and%20the%20person%20in%20front%20of%20the%20patrol%20saw%20some%20movement%20on%20top%20of%20a%20hill.%20It%20was%20an%20observation%20post%20(OP)%2C%20and%20around%20two%20Maoists%20were%20present.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maoists%20were%20armed%20with%20Kalashnikovs%2C%20Light%20Machine%20Guns%2C%20rifles%20like%20INSAS%2C%20and%20other%20automatic%20weapons.%20In%20an%20uphill%20battle%2C%20the%20ratio%20is%20usually%2010%3A1%2C%20i.e.%2C%20if%201%20enemy%20is%20present%2C%20then%20at%20least%2010%20soldiers%20are%20needed%20for%20an%20attack.%20The%20troops%20from%20DRG%20and%20BSF%20meticulously%20planned%20their%20ascent%20and%20surrounded%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fsmdrpfbg_chhattisgarh-maoist-encounter_625x300_17_April_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20team%20camouflaged%20with%20the%20surroundings%20and%20cornered%20them%20to%20lay%20a%20cordon.%20We%20knew%20they'd%20run%20for%20cover%2C%20and%20when%20they%20ran%20to%20protect%20themselves%2C%20they%20opened%20fire%2C%20and%20our%20teams%20retaliated%20with%20a%20heavy%20response%2C%20and%20the%20dense%20jungle%20turned%20into%20a%20battleground%2C%26quot%3B%20Sub%20Inspector%20Chaudhary%20recalled%20how%20the%20operation%20panned%20out.%20The%20officer%20hails%20from%20Jaipur%2C%20and%20his%20family%20is%20present%20with%20him%20in%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brave%20soldier%20twirled%20his%20moustache%20when%20Chhattisgarh%20Chief%20Minister%20Vijay%20Sharma%20met%20him%20at%20the%20hospital.%20The%20smile%20on%20the%20officer's%20face%20did%20not%20fade%20despite%20being%20injured.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Maoists%20Used%20A%20Dangerous%20Tactic'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20gun%20battle%20was%20on%2C%20and%20I%20took%20cover%20behind%20a%20tree.%20They%20fired%20back%20to%20break%20the%20ambush%20to%20run%20away%2C%20but%20a%20burst%20of%20fire%20from%20an%20LMG%20came%20and%20hit%20my%20leg.%20Even%20after%20getting%20hit%2C%20I%20could%20observe%20and%20tell%20my%20troops%20and%20told%20them%20that%20the%20Maoists%20were%20lying%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20using%20automatic%20weapons.%20It's%20a%20very%20dangerous%20tactic%20they%20used%20against%20us%20as%20the%20target%20becomes%20small%20when%20you%20lie%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuryakant%20Shrimali%2C%20a%20personnel%20from%20the%20DRG%2C%20was%20also%20injured%20in%20the%20encounter.%20He%20recalled%20how%20his%20team%20laid%20a%20cordon%20from%20two%20sides%20to%20ambush%20the%20Maoists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F4rtbso9g_suryakant-shrimali-drg_625x300_17_April_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'We%20Ate%20Fruits'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20crossed%20the%20river%20and%20got%20information%20that%20around%2025%20Maoists%20were%20present%2C%20climbed%20the%20hill%20and%20crossed%20a%20river%20stream%20but%20couldn't%20locate%20them.%20We%20ate%20fruits%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20Tuesday%20and%20then%20moved%20forward%20with%20our%20search.%20We%20received%20inputs%20that%20in%20Alparas%20forests%20around%2030%20Maoists%20are%20present%20on%20top%20of%20the%20hill.%20I%20was%20in%20the%20Tango%20company.%20We%20laid%20a%20cordon%20and%20ambushed%20them%20and%20the%20battle%20began%20around%20noon%20and%20went%20on%20for%20almost%20four%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20Suryakant%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20hit%20in%20the%20right%20leg%20and%20it%20went%20through%20and%20through.%20We%20were%20determined%20to%20complete%20the%20operation%20and%20we%20finished%20their%20party.%20The%20operation%20was%20a%20big%20success%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713363960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fairka58_sub-inspector-bsf-chhattisgarh-_625x300_17_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-soldier-account-how-massive-chhattisgarh-anti-maoist-op-was-executed-5463315%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20the%20night%20of%20April%2015%2C%20a%20search%20party%20from%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%20and%20the%20District%20Reserve%20Guard%20(DRG)%20were%20on%20patrol%20in%20the%20dense%20jungles%20of%20Hapatola%20in%20the%20Kanker%20district%20of%20Chhattisgarh%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-soldier-account-how-massive-chhattisgarh-anti-maoist-op-was-executed-5463315%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-soldier-account-how-massive-chhattisgarh-anti-maoist-op-was-executed-5463315%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-soldier-account-how-massive-chhattisgarh-anti-maoist-op-was-executed-5463315%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Viral%20YouTuber%20Angry%20Rantman%20dies%20at%2027%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713363240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F04%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-angry-rantman-india_6524488.png%3F202404171612