%20to%20be%20treated%20like%20this.%20They%20feel%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20right%20to%20the%20good%20things.%20Watching%20these%20patterns%20change%20and%20overcoming%20these%20thoughts%20and%20misconceptions%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20rewarding%20experiences%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Robin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20classes%2C%20every%20Krantikari%20has%20to%20do%20two%20extracurricular%20activities%20%E2%80%94%20one%20physical%20and%20one%20artistic%20%E2%80%94%20choosing%20from%20karate%2C%20music%2C%20dance%2C%20photography%2C%20drums%20and%20many%20more.%20The%20theatre%20also%20forms%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20every%20girl%E2%80%99s%20life%2C%20and%20they%20use%20this%20art%20form%20to%20share%20the%20story%20of%20sex%20workers%E2%80%99%20lives%20with%20people%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKranti%E2%80%99s%20play%2C%20%E2%80%98Lal%20Batti%20Express%E2%80%99%2C%20has%20been%20performed%20across%20India%2C%20the%20US%20and%20the%20UK.%20The%20girls%20also%20travel%20and%20conduct%20workshops%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-19.44.56-10-min-1713281617.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Theatre%20is%20a%20major%20focus%20area%20at%20Kranti%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-19.44.56-10-min-1713281617.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-19.44.56-10-min-1713281617-300x199.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-19.44.56-10-min-1713281617-500x332.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-19.44.56-10-min-1713281617-768x510.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-19.44.56-10-min-1713281617-1536x1020.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-19.44.56-10-min-1713281617-150x100.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-19.44.56-10-min-1713281617-272x182.jpeg%20272w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347430%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221062%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETheatre%20is%20a%20major%20focus%20area%20at%20Kranti%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKranti%20has%20helped%20over%2027%20girls%20so%20far%2C%20with%20almost%2022%20of%20them%20going%20to%20university.%20The%20biggest%20win%20for%20Robin%20though%2C%20has%20been%20the%20fact%20that%20all%20of%20them%20have%20found%20their%20calling%20in%20social%20change.%20None%20of%20them%20want%20to%20just%20%E2%80%9Cbecome%20rich%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cown%20a%20BMW%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20Robin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20beautiful%20part%20for%20me%20has%20been%20seeing%20them%20grow%20as%20human%20beings.%20Everyone%20is%20working%20on%20studying%20either%20special%20needs%20education%2C%20gender%20studies%2C%20nursing%2C%20counselling%2C%20or%20psychology.%20They%20have%20all%20found%20their%20niche%20in%20social%20change.%20They%20have%20understood%20their%20purpose%2C%20which%20is%20to%20be%20able%20to%20support%20others%20through%20their%20journeys%20of%20healing%20and%20overcoming%20adversity%2C%20which%20makes%20me%20incredibly%20proud%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20social%20activist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20like%20Sandhya%20are%20working%20with%20NGOs%20like%20Save%20the%20Child%20Foundation%2C%20while%20others%20like%20Shweta%20have%20returned%20to%20Kranti%20as%20employees.%3C%2