n%20from%20him%20as%20he%20believed%20that%20this%20was%20a%20waste%20of%20time%2C%20he%20gave%20me%20three-acre%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarishchandra%20sold%20off%20that%20land%20and%20bought%20new%20land%20in%20Village%20Budhoda%20in%20the%20Ausa%20block%20of%20Latur%20district%2C%20which%20now%20holds%20the%20Grameen%20Shramik%20Pratishthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20fighting%20the%20society%20and%20his%20family%20to%20start%20the%20organisation%2C%20Harishchandra%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20the%20first%20person%20to%20graduate%20from%20college.%20I%20could%20have%20just%20stuck%20to%20a%20job%20and%20%E2%80%98given%20back%E2%80%99%20to%20my%20family%2C%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20my%20education%20to%20give%20back%20to%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFoundation%20of%20the%20NGO%20%26amp%3B%20how%20you%20can%20help%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarishchandra%20has%20spent%20decades%20of%20his%20life%20caring%20for%20the%20underserved.%20His%20son%20Prashant%20Sude%20is%20following%20in%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20footsteps%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20still%20works%20and%20stays%20every%20day%2C%20but%20I%20have%20now%20taken%20over%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20organisation.%20There%20are%20a%20few%20levels%20of%20interventions%20that%20we%20do%20to%20help%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%20works%20to%20help%20people%20with%20disabilities%20by%20giving%20them%20training%20in%20different%20areas%20to%20help%20them%20become%20independent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20our%20Swadhar%20Scheme%2C%20what%20we%20initially%20did%20was%20train%20them%20in%20recycling%20old%20%3Cem%3Esarees%20%3C%2Fem%3Einto%20mats.%20The%20disposal%20of%20old%20%3Cem%3Esarees%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20a%20significant%20issue%2C%20contributing%20to%20environmental%20harm.%20At%20our%20hand-me-down%20centre%2C%20we%20recycle%20these%20sarees%20