ually%20skilled%20if%20given%20the%20right%20set%20of%20opportunities%2C%20but%20they%20are%20neglected%20often%20by%20their%20own%20family.%20With%20Swadhaar%2C%20we%20are%20aiming%20to%20reduce%20this%20gap%20by%20presenting%20them%20with%20the%20right%20opportunities.%20We%20want%20to%20help%20them%20become%20independent%2C%20self-sustaining%2C%20and%20live%20the%20life%20they%20deserve%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prashant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHarishchandra%20and%20Prashant%E2%80%99s%20fight%20to%20give%20equal%20rights%20to%20people%20with%20disabilities%20does%20not%20have%20to%20be%20theirs%20alone.%20You%20can%20contribute%20to%20their%20cause%20too.%20Click%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpages.razorpay.com%2Fpl_F40P3oSEKNjVkq%2Fview%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20to%20do%20your%20part.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%20and%20Pranita%20Bhat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(All%20pictures%20credit%3A%20Prashant%20Sude)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713278320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D346821%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20child%2C%20Harishchandra%20Sude%20lost%20vision%20in%20one%20eye%20and%20encountered%20prejudice.%20Despite%20this%2C%20he%20dedicated%20himself%20to%20creating%20change%2C%20establishing%20Grameen%20Shramik%20Pratishthan%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20which%20provides%20skill-based%20training%20to%20individuals%20with%20visual%20impairment%20and%20disabilities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346821%2Fharishchandra-sude-prashant-sude-maharashtra-ngo-that-helps-people-with-disability-training%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Flights%20diverted%20at%20one%20of%20world's%20busiest%20airports%20after%20year's%20rainfall%20in%20a%20day%22%2C%