f%20operations.%20Kinara%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20such%20conditions%20and%20gave%20us%20a%20loan%2C%20which%20helped%20us%20immensely.%20The%20entire%20process%20was%20streamlined%20and%20online.%20An%20officer%20from%20their%20team%20came%20for%20inspection%20and%20sanctioned%20the%20loan%20very%20quickly%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDivya%20has%20been%20able%20to%20grow%20her%20company%20to%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%203%20crores%20in%203%20years.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20all%20this%2C%20Hardika%20states%20that%20Kinara%20is%20profitable%20today%20and%20rearing%20to%20reach%20more%20business%20owners.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20for%20Kinara%E2%80%99s%20existence%20began%20thanks%20to%20a%20woman%20entrepreneur%2C%20and%20hence%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20no-brainer%20that%20their%20HerVikas%20programme%2C%20which%20offers%20discounts%20to%20women%20entrepreneurs%20to%20boost%20their%20businesses%2C%20remains%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20has%20disbursed%20Rs%20700%20crores%20in%20the%20past%205%20years%2C%20offering%20a%201%20percent%20interest%20discount%2C%2060%20day%20repayment%20holiday%2C%2050%20reduction%20in%20processing%20fees.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%203.5%20percent%20to%204%20percent%20Non-Performing%20Asset%20(NPA)%20rate%2C%20Hardika%20wants%20to%20reach%20more%20MSMEs%20in%20the%20coming%20years%2C%20hoping%20to%20reach%202%20lakh%20additional%20customers%20in%20the%20next%203%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20notion%20that%20unsecured%20business%20lending%20is%20risky%20and%20customers%20will%20disappear%20with%20your%20money.%20Our%20numbers%20prove%20that%20this%20is%20so%20far%20away%20from%20the%20truth.%20Customers%20are%20grateful%20to%20have%20access%20to%20capital%20and%20repay%20on%20time.%20They%20also%20use%20the%20money%20judiciously%20to%20grow%20their%20businesses%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20sh