its%20right%20beside%20Beas%20River.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20place%20even%20has%20a%20natural%20spring%20on%20the%20property.%20%E2%80%9CBack%20in%20the%20day%20when%20we%20were%20growing%20up%2C%20you%20could%20simply%20open%20a%20tap%2C%20stick%20your%20face%20under%20it%2C%20and%20drink%20water%2C%20right%3F%20Here%2C%20you%20can%20do%20exactly%20that!%20The%20taps%20are%20connected%20to%20the%20natural%20spring%20water%20and%20you%20can%20drink%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20enjoying%20nature%2C%20guests%20can%20also%20indulge%20in%20the%20delicious%20meals%20that%20Shalini%20prepares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20lots%20of%20edible%20weeds%20growing%20on%20the%20property.%20So%2C%20my%20favourite%20thing%20is%20to%20pick%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20what%20is%20growing%20in%20the%20garden.%20Locally%2C%20they%20grow%20%3Cem%3Eurad%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(black%20gram)%20and%20make%20little%20dried%20%3Cem%3Ebadis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(vegetable%20nuggets)%20out%20of%20it%20for%20winter%2C%20because%20nothing%20grows%20here%20in%20the%20cold%20weather.%20So%2C%20they%20dry%20whatever%20they%20grow%20in%20summer%20or%20make%20these%20%3Cem%3Ebadis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20keep%20them.%20I%20love%20serving%20my%20guests%20these%20%3Cem%3Ebadis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20zucchini-based%20dishes%20because%20it%20grows%20here%20in%20abundance.%20We%20prepare%20it%20in%20various%20ways.%20There%20are%20also%20local%20dishes%20like%20%3Cem%3Esiddu%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20is%20like%20a%20bao%20stuffed%20with%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShalini%20also%20uses%20fiddlehead%20fern%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F248547%2Fhomemade-pickles-athey-nallatha-hafez-rahman-akshay-raveendran-kerala-homemakers-san196%2F%5C%