2578444-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-10-1-1712578444-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346808%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%20offers%20delicious%20meals%20like%20siddu%2C%20badi%2C%20and%20homemade%20pickles.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20construction%20materials%2C%20most%20buildings%20in%20the%20hills%20are%20built%20with%20wood%20as%20it%20is%20a%20good%20insulating%20material.%20%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20incorporated%20insulating%20blocks%20in%20the%20construction%2C%20which%20further%20reduce%20heating%20and%20air%20conditioning%20costs.%20These%20blocks%20are%20light%20enough%20to%20float%20on%20water%20and%20insulate%20the%20entire%20building.%20Furthermore%2C%20all%20windows%20are%20double-glazed%20with%20argon%20gas%20in%20between%20for%20additional%20insulation%2C%20and%20the%20roofs%20are%20insulated%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20heating%2C%20the%20property%20utilises%20geothermal%20heat%20pumps%2C%20tapping%20into%20a%20spring%20on%20the%20property%20for%20ground%20source%20water.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20water%2C%20naturally%20warm%20in%20winter%2C%20is%20cycled%20through%20the%20geothermal%20heat%20pump%20to%20extract%20heat%2C%20which%20is%20then%20used%20to%20heat%20the%20building.%20Underfloor%20pipes%2C%20spanning%20almost%20a%20kilometre%2C%20distribute%20this%20heat%20throughout%20the%20building%2C%20providing%20an%20efficient%20heating%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nitin%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20faced%20several%20power%20cuts%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20be%20more%20sustainable%20and%20go%20solar.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20run%20our%20operations%20entirely%20on%20solar%20power.%20We%20have%20a%20solar%20system%20in%20place%20that%20generates%20electricity%2C%20and%20our%20entire%20house%20runs%20on%20this.%20Even%20on%20days%20when%20there%E2%80%99s%20as%20little%20as%2030%25%20sunlight%2C%20the%20system%20works%20efficiently.%20Additionally%2C%20any%20excess%20energy%20generated%20during%20the%20day%20is%20stored%20in%20batteries%2C%20which%20we%20then%20use%20for%20power%20backup%20when%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20six%20years%20of%20operations%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20hosted%20countless%20number%20of%20happy%20guests%20so%20far.%20Among%20them%20is%20Mumbai-based%20Priyanka%20who%20stayed%20at%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLocated%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Beas%20River%2C%20Shalini%20and%20Nitin%E2%80%99s%20homestay%20exceeded%20all%20our%20expectations.%20Surrounded%20by%20beautiful%20fruit%20trees%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20season%20you%20visit%2C%20you%20can%20indulge%20in%20farm-fresh%20fruits%20every%20day!%E2%80%9D%20she%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsIpyiWSH3A%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsIpyiWSH3A%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%